    <p>Many Faculties and academic departments run international programming for students during the spring/summer term. For more information about this type of programming visit our section on&nbsp;<a href="/content/ryerson/global-learning/abroad/step1/faculty-led.html">Faculty-Led Programs.</a></p>
    





